tle_font_size=\"16px\"]\n\nAny scrutiny like a management issue will succumb under our control if you will choose our interim management specialists to take over..\n\n[/tm_pb_toggle][tm_pb_toggle admin_label=\"Toggle\" title=\"Business plan consulting\" open=\"off\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" open_toggle_background_color=\"#15c1c6\" closed_toggle_background_color=\"#333333\" title_font=\"Merriweather|on|||\" title_text_color=\"#ffffff\" body_font_size=\"16px\" title_font_size=\"16px\"]\n\nAre you about to pitch a plan for angel\'s funding? Or you\'ve started it all with your principal capital at stake? We can help to plan it all out.\n\n[/tm_pb_toggle][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"on\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" custom_padding=\"||50px|\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||30px|\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" custom_padding=\"||25px|\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ebebeb\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_style=\"solid\"] [/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"20px|||\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|\"]\n<h5>Tabs</h5>\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_tabs admin_label=\"Tabs\" active_tab_background_color=\"#15c1c6\" inactive_tab_background_color=\"#333333\" tab_text_color=\"#ffffff\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#ebebeb\" border_style=\"solid\" tab_font=\"Merriweather|on|||\" tab_font_size=\"16\" body_font_size=\"16\" saved_tabs=\"all\"] [tm_pb_tab title=\"Assessment\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]\n\nFirstly we received access to all documentation, reports and structure of the company. We analyzed the current and yearly performance, sales, staff flow for the hayford company... <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full\" src=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg\" width=\"1098\" height=\"586\" />\n\n[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title=\"Business strategy\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]\n\nThe next step was to draft a business strategy for business\' future deelopment over a period of 2, 5 and 10 years. We always aim to correlate our recommendations with the vision each company offers, when we\'re composing such a strategy... <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full\" src=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg\" width=\"1098\" height=\"586\" />\n\n[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title=\"HR optimization\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]\n\nAn optimized business always starts with the team optimization. That is the reason we do the human resources diligence and file our suggestions to the board. <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full\" src=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg\" width=\"1098\" height=\"586\" />\n\n[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title=\"Processes optimization\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]\n\nBusiness processes optimization is the most vital instrument when we aim to turn the company around. We always sketch and implement such overhauls in a close cooperation with company\'s top management. <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full\" src=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg\" width=\"1098\" height=\"586\" />\n\n[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title=\"Market research\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]\n\nBeing one of the most competitive out there, we had conducted multiple researches and we arranged an extensive overhaul for the marketing department of the company. <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full\" src=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg\" width=\"1098\" height=\"586\" />\n\n[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title=\"Year-by-year analysis\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]\n\nAfter out initial job\'s been implemented, the next thing we did is a year-by-year analysis. Since year one and during all 6 years we\'ve been advising hayford company shown a significant surge both in sales and market value. <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1463 size-full\" src=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg\" width=\"1098\" height=\"586\" />\n\n[/tm_pb_tab] [/tm_pb_tabs][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"on\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" custom_padding=\"||50px|\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||30px|\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" custom_padding=\"||25px|\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ebebeb\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_style=\"solid\"] [/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"40px|||\" custom_margin_tablet=\"20px|||\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|tablet\"]\n<h5>Contact form</h5>\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make