(193, 1, '2016-06-02 09:18:09', '2016-06-02 09:18:09', '[tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\" template_type=\"row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Resources planning\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon01.png\" custom_margin=\"||60px|\"]\n\n<p>With the pace manpower switches jobs these days, we will keep your business packed with pros only!</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Interim managers\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon04.png\"]\n\n<p>Any scrutiny like a management issue will succumb under our control if you will choose our...</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Strategic planning\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon02.png\"]\n\n<p>Building a strategic development and expansion plan is vital, as the tactics game will simply leave...</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Market research\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon05.png\"]\n\n<p>It\'s impossible to succeed in business these days, regardless of the niche, without a proper... marketing team and researching</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Conflict management\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/icon03.png\"]\n\n<p>Big business means a lot of people in one place. Looks like a recipe for disaster?</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Exit planning\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" 