(1052, 1, '2016-06-28 09:38:05', '2016-06-28 09:38:05', '[tm_pb_tabs admin_label=\"Tabs\" active_tab_background_color=\"#49d376\" inactive_tab_background_color=\"#333333\" tab_text_color=\"#ffffff\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#ebebeb\" border_style=\"solid\" tab_font=\"Merriweather|on|||\" tab_font_size=\"16\" body_font_size=\"16\" saved_tabs=\"all\" custom_css_main_element=\"max-width: 1190px;||margin: auto;\" template_type=\"module\"]\n\n[tm_pb_tab title=\"Assessment\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]<p>Firstly we received access to all documentation, reports and structure of the company.<br> We analyzed the current and yearly performance, sales, staff flow for the hayford company...</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208\" src=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/elements-12.jpg\" alt=\"elements-12\" width=\"1098\" height=\"586\"></p>[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title=\"Business strategy\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]<p>The next step was to draft a business strategy for business\' future deelopment over a period of 2, 5 and 10 years.<br> We always aim to correlate our recommendations with the vision each company offers, when we\'re composing such a strategy...</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-75\" src=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img09.jpg\" alt=\"img09\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p>[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title=\"HR optimization\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]<p>An optimized business always starts with the team optimization.<br> That is the reason we do the human resources diligence and file our suggestions to the board.</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-77\" src=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img01.jpg\" alt=\"img01\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\"></p>[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title=\"Processes optimization\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]<p>Business processes optimization is the most vital instrument when we aim to turn the company around.<br> We always sketch and implement such overhauls in a close cooperation with company\'s top management.</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-73\" src=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img07.jpg\" alt=\"img07\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\"></p>[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title=\"Market research\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]<p>Being one of the most competitive out there, we had conducted multiple researches and we arranged an extensive overhaul for the marketing department of the company.</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-69\" src=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img03.jpg\" alt=\"img03\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\"></p>[/tm_pb_tab][tm_pb_tab title=\"Year-by-year analysis\" tab_font_select=\"default\" tab_font=\"||||\" tab_line_height=\"2em\" tab_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" tab_line_height_phone=\"2em\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" body_line_height=\"2em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"2em\" body_line_height_phone=\"2em\"]<p>After out initial job\'s been implemented, the next thing we did is a year-by-year analysis.<br> Since year one and during all 6 years we\'ve been advising hayford company shown a significant surge both in sales and market value.</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-81\" src=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img11.jpg\" alt=\"img11\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\"></p>[/tm_pb_tab]\n\n[/tm_pb_tabs]', 'Tabs', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tabs', '', '', '2016-06-28 09:38:05', '2016-06-28 09:38:05', '', 0, 'http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/tm_pb_layout/tabs/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0),
(1174, 1, '2016-07-25 15:55:18', '2016-07-25 15:55:18', '[tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"on\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" custom_padding=\"90px||100px|\" custom_padding_tablet=\"50px||50px|\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" template_type=\"section\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Сore values</h3><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #2da5ee;\">and our advantages</span></h2>\n\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Complex Approach\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#ebebeb\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/about-number01.png\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" saved_tabs=\"all\"]\n\n<p>We are positive that the end goal of increasing your value can be achieved only through diligent managing all possible aspects of your portfolio, such as assets, property, real estate, businesses and everything else... That makes our investment company one of the few on the market, who recognize the need to go full-cycle!ting.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Safe Bets\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#ebebeb\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/about-number02.png\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" saved_tabs=\"all\"]\n\n<p>When it comes to a dangerous and risky business of investing, we take an approach that is data-scientific and risks-proof. The precision with which our team of experts manages to arrive at the best advice for managing your assets and money is worldwiade known and is proven by the  portfolio of our impressive clients!</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Adaptable projections\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#ebebeb\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/about-number03.png\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"off|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" saved_tabs=\"all\"]\n\n<p>With all the volatility that a modern business faces and with all the pressure that just keeps on hitting, sticking to a short-term financial projection for too long is too dangerous... Once again, taking a scientific-like approach to data analysis, we are able to predict when the time comes to change either the tactics or the strategies of your mind game.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section]', 'blurb(number)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'blurbnumber', '', '', '2016-07-25 15:55:18', '2016-07-25 15:55:18', '', 0, 'http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/tm_pb_layout/blurbnumber/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0),
