con_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" header_font_size=\"66\" header_font_size_tablet=\"46\" header_font_size_phone=\"36\" header_font_size_last_edited=\"on|phone\" header_text_color=\"#ffffff\" body_text_color=\"#ffffff\" body_line_height=\"1.4em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"1.4em\" body_line_height_phone=\"1.4em\"]<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The trick is, that some of them indeed are, while other are plummeting in a downward spiral of a market... That\'s why you need an investments advisor, a person who will tell you right financial decisions from wrong financial mistakes...</p>[/tm_pb_slide][tm_pb_slide heading=\"Set your own pace\" button_text=\"Read more\" button_link=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/about-us/\" background_image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/slide02.jpg\" background_position=\"default\" background_size=\"cover\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" alignment=\"center\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" text_border_radius=\"3\" header_font_select=\"Merriweather\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_font_select=\"default\" button_font=\"||||\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" header_font_size=\"66\" header_font_size_tablet=\"46\" header_font_size_phone=\"36\" header_font_size_last_edited=\"on|phone\" header_text_color=\"#ffffff\" body_text_color=\"#ffffff\" body_line_height=\"1.4em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"1.4em\" body_line_height_phone=\"1.4em\"]<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We are confident about the fact, that clear goals, a long-term investment philosophy, a balanced portfolio, and low costs create a path to your financial goals. There\'s investing, and there\'s smart investing. We\'re the latter, we\'re better!</p>[/tm_pb_slide][tm_pb_slide heading=\"Why You Need an Advisor?\" button_text=\"Read more\" button_link=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/about-us/\" background_image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/slide03.jpg\" background_position=\"default\" background_size=\"cover\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" alignment=\"center\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" text_border_radius=\"3\" header_font_select=\"Merriweather\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_font_select=\"default\" button_font=\"||||\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" header_font_size=\"66\" header_font_size_tablet=\"46\" header_font_size_phone=\"36\" header_font_size_last_edited=\"on|phone\" header_text_color=\"#ffffff\" body_text_color=\"#ffffff\" body_line_height=\"1.4em\" body_line_height_tablet=\"1.4em\" body_line_height_phone=\"1.4em\"]<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We help you in creating a financial strategy that represents your personality. Getting to know you is financial advisor’s primary goal. - An approach centered around your life’s priorities. It’s time for a financial strategy that puts your needs and priorities front and center.</p>[/tm_pb_slide]\n\n[/tm_pb_slider][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row]', 'hayford_slider', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hayford_slider', '', '', '2016-07-25 16:02:40', '2016-07-25 16:02:40', '', 0, 'http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/tm_pb_layout/hayford_slider/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0);
