rucks and offers a broad range of services for the over-the-road, construction, municipal and medium duty markets.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Richard White\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo08.png\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" header_text_color=\"#2da5ee\" custom_margin=\"||60px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" url=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/cases/richard-white/\"]\n\n<p>BenQ Corporation is a Taiwanese multi-national company that sells and markets technology products, consumer electronics, computing.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Compact\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo09.png\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" header_text_color=\"#2da5ee\" custom_margin=\"||60px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" url=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/cases/compact/\"]\n\n<p>Compaq was a company founded in 1982, offerings include Presario notebooks and laptop PCs, desktops and computer accessories.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Bingo\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo10.png\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" header_text_color=\"#2da5ee\" custom_margin=\"||60px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" url=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/cases/bingo/\"]\n\n<p>That\'s just one of the hardware/software industry leaders whom we consult on business strategic planning...</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Be Clener\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo11.png\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" header_text_color=\"#2da5ee\" custom_margin=\"||60px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" url=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/cases/be-clener/\"]\n\n<p>Maxdata was a German company that produced IT products, such as computers, notebooks and monitors.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Domino\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" image=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/logo12.png\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" header_text_color=\"#2da5ee\" custom_margin=\"||60px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" url=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/cases/domino/\"]\n\n<p>It\'s one of our oldest returning clients. Their year-by-year growth, achieved in big part thanks to our advice, is the reason.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section]', 'cases_hayford', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cases_hayford', '', '', '2016-07-26 15:50:22', '2016-07-26 15:50:22', '', 0, 'http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/tm_pb_layout/cases_hayford/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0),
