(1649, 1, '2016-12-29 08:54:29', '2016-12-29 08:54:29', '[tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"off\" parallax_4=\"off\" parallax_method_4=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\" template_type=\"row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Damien Kaschzmarek\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team1.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\n<p>Damien was appointed as Managing Director of our Investments venture in February 2014, after 4 years as Chief Executive Officer.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Derek Zoolander\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team2.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\n<p>Derek joined us in 2007, has been Company Secretary since 2010 and was appointed Chief Operating Officer in 2015. He is a Chartered Accountant.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Tom Marvolo\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team3.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||45px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\n<p>He has over 30 years’ experience in financial and investment accounting and has extensive experience in the management of the portfolio...</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"James Potter\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team4.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\n<p>Mr. Potter joined us in 2010 as an Investment Analyst and was promoted to Senior Investment Officer. He has long experience as an analyst.</p>\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row]', 'PERSONE', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'persone', '', '', '2016-12-29 08:54:29', '2016-12-29 08:54:29', '', 0, 'http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/tm_pb_layout/persone/', 0, 'tm_pb_layout', '', 0),
