(1735, 1, '2020-03-25 01:16:18', '2020-03-24 22:16:18', '[tm_pb_section admin_label=\"section\" background_image=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/image32.jpg\" transparent_background=\"on\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" custom_padding=\"375px||375px|\" custom_padding_tablet=\"200px||200px|\" custom_padding_phone=\"100px||100px|\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"on\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" custom_padding=\"100px|||\" custom_padding_tablet=\"50px|||\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"When we decided to set up our operations 25 years ago, we had a list of principles that we all stood by, as co-founders...\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#ebebeb\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"off|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" saved_tabs=\"all\"]\n\nThey did not change a bit. It was and still is a distinct desire to deliver complex, 360° investment consulting services, that would fill any gap in any business\' daily, monthly and yearly operations. With that in mind, we continue to implement our expertise to help hundreds of companies!\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"With the help of our advisors hundreds of small, medium and big companies were able to achieve results, such as:\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#ebebeb\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"off|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" saved_tabs=\"all\"]\n\n<span style=\"color: #15c1cb;\">1) Steady year-by-year growth</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #15c1cb;\">2) Spring back from a recession or market value drop</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #15c1cb;\">3) Ill-conceived IPO turned into a golden share IPO</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #15c1cb;\">4) Investments risks eliminated, billions of dollars spent more efficiently</span>\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"on\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" custom_padding=\"90px||100px|\" custom_padding_tablet=\"50px||50px|\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Why Choosing</h3>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #15c1cb;\">Us is a Smart Move</span></h2>\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Full Cycle Biz Management\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#ebebeb\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/num1.png\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" saved_tabs=\"all\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\"]\n\nOur strong conviction is that if a business is to be optimized, it\'s to be optimized in a full cycle manner! Our expertise spans from business and investment consulting and well into HR/recruiting and M&amp;A fields...\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Low-risk Strategy\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#ebebeb\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/num2.png\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" saved_tabs=\"all\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\"]\n<div id=\"u667\" class=\"ax_default heading_1\">\n<div id=\"u668\" class=\"text\">\n\nWe clearly understand, that you want not to lose, but to earn more money over your period of work with us. That\'s why we reject all high-risk endeavors, that may lead to a fast stack of cash for the first time but to a principal capital\'s loss the second time.. We base our advice only on low-risk operations and estimates.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Fast &amp; Efficient\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#49d376\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#333333\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#49d376\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#ebebeb\" border_style=\"solid\" image=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/num3.png\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"off|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||30px|\" saved_tabs=\"all\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\"]\n<div id=\"u671\" class=\"ax_default heading_1\">\n<div id=\"u672\" class=\"text\">\n\nDue diligence is one thing. But we\'re trying to deliver the most fast paced business assessments diligence in the industry. While working with us, your business will never get stuck in the middle of the road with no spare tires in the back...\n\n</div>\n</div>\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"on\" parallax_method=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" background_color=\"#49d376\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"off|phone\" background_image=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/image33.jpg\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\" custom_padding=\"80px||40px|\" custom_padding_tablet=\"30px||40px|\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_circle_counter admin_label=\"Circle Counter\" title=\"Median y-b-y growth our clients businesses show\" number=\"9\" percent_sign=\"on\" rounded_bar=\"on\" circle_width=\"4\" circle_size=\"238\" bar_bg_color=\"#15c1cb\" title_font=\"Merriweather|on|||\" title_font_size=\"18\" title_text_color=\"#ffffff\" number_font=\"Merriweather|on|||\" number_text_color=\"#ffffff\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" circle_color_alpha=\"1\"] [/tm_pb_circle_counter][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_circle_counter admin_label=\"Circle Counter\" title=\"Median sales rise after 5 years of our services\" number=\"89\" percent_sign=\"on\" rounded_bar=\"on\" circle_width=\"4\" circle_size=\"238\" bar_bg_color=\"#15c1cb\" title_font=\"Merriweather|on|||\" title_font_size=\"18\" title_text_color=\"#ffffff\" number_font=\"Merriweather|on|||\" number_text_color=\"#ffffff\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" circle_color_alpha=\"1\"] [/tm_pb_circle_counter][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_circle_counter admin_label=\"Circle Counter\" title=\"Number of our returning clients\" number=\"99\" percent_sign=\"on\" rounded_bar=\"on\" circle_width=\"4\" circle_size=\"238\" bar_bg_color=\"#15c1cb\" title_font=\"Merriweather|on|||\" title_font_size=\"18\" title_text_color=\"#ffffff\" number_font=\"Merriweather|on|||\" number_text_color=\"#ffffff\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" circle_color_alpha=\"1\"] [/tm_pb_circle_counter][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"on\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" custom_padding=\"80px||40px|\" custom_padding_tablet=\"50px||40px|\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Meet</h3>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #15c1cb;\">the Team</span></h2>\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" parallax_3=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"off\" parallax_4=\"off\" parallax_method_4=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Damien Kaschzmarek\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team1.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nDamien was appointed as Managing Director of our Investments venture in February 2014, after 4 years as Chief Executive Officer.\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Derek Zoolander\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team2.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nDerek joined us in 2007, has been Company Secretary since 2010 and was appointed Chief Operating Officer in 2015. He is a Chartered Accountant.\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Tom Marvolo\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team3.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||45px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nHe has over 30 years’ experience in financial and investment accounting and has extensive experience in the management of the portfolio...\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"James Potter\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team4.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nMr. Potter joined us in 2010 as an Investment Analyst and was promoted to Senior Investment Officer. He has long experience as an analyst.\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Lily Granger\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team5.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nWhile Lily works here only 10 years, her efficiency allowed us to name her a Senior manager of our biggest portfolios...\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Timothy Dumbledore\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team6.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nWhat Timothy does to company\'s, is what our clients call \"fiscal magic\". He is an accomplished pro regarding any investing gamble...\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Lionel Hollande\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team7.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nLionel has joined us after years of consulting for Wall Street’s biggest financial institutions. He studied economics at Harvard University.\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Craig Ferguson\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team8.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nPrior to joining our agencyt, Craig worked at JPMorgan for 10 years in Credit Markets and Risk Technology. He is a CERTIFIED PLANNER™...\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Diane Mist\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team9.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nBefore joining our experts\' vast team, Diane was the Behavioral Finance Specialist at Barclays Americas and London teams in 2007.\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Andrew Cuomo\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team10.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nWith a background in global bond markets, Andrew\'s outlook on our fixed income exposures is invaluable and priceless...\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Ben Edwards\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team11.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nBen is one of the worlds strongest advocates of value investing, and assists us with asset allocation models he developed...\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Chris Cripsie\" image_url=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/team12.jpg\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" header_text_color=\"#333333\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||50px|\" header_font=\"Merriweather||||\" header_font_size=\"26\" header_line_height=\"1.3em\" saved_tabs=\"all\" text_alignment=\"left\"]\n\nChris brings deep experience in equity trading from his days at Goldman Sachs, advising on the nuance of tax and execution risks...\n\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" background_image=\"http://wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image30.jpg\" transparent_background=\"on\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" custom_margin_tablet=\"30px|||\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"off|desktop\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_cta admin_label=\"Call To Action\" button_url=\"http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_52382-sample/contacts/\" url_new_window=\"off\" button_text=\"Careers\" use_background_color=\"off\" background_color=\"#49d376\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_